{"tid":1018023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隨機問美國女學生：願不願意和我兒約會　支那大媽慘被通緝","createTime":"2019-02-12T02:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T03:36:47.000Z","uid":32511,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b6482583fb8198f2362aa8dcadcc83e727b79f3d","tid":1018023,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"美國馬里蘭州陶森大學（Towson University）日前出現一名疑似中國人的亞裔婦女，在校園內閒晃，同時拿著兒子的照片，詢問女學生願不願意跟她兒子約會。事後女學生們嚇到報警，目前大媽已遭到通緝。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這名大媽於2月6日、7日（大年初二、三）拿著兒子的照片到陶森大學，詢問路過的女學生願不願意和她兒子約會。許多女學生被大媽舉動嚇到報警，目前警方已將大媽通緝，並表示若找到人，不會對她起訴，僅規勸她不要再騷擾學生。<br />\n<br />\n事情曝光後，引發網友熱議，美國網友指出，中國家長常常在大城市公園內替兒女找對象，這大媽應該是趁過年，到美國探望兒子時，順便幫忙找對象；中國網友則說，「外國人畢竟見識少」、「有這樣的母親，兒子就是媽寶」。"},{"pid":"eefe16cca3389d822dfcaf5145f754c56f10a19d","tid":1018023,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:03:40.000Z","msg":"幫個仔搵母雞"},{"pid":"b302ea7cfb2a8076e363505947717494eeff12ca","tid":1018023,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"龜婆"},{"pid":"1c2bc45aa171f927bda16a0e416ee3dfbe8b68b4","tid":1018023,"uid":63154,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:09:01.000Z","msg":"唔去中國搵？要美國搵？用意明顯啦，為咗娶個美國妹一家移民咋，評論個網友明顯都係中國人啦，講到咁平常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834e87fa6ee4f4025ab546675d353763752e474f","tid":1018023,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"傑出華人系列 又再一次揚威海外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e20e763b7bf57af999db37689268808fcf7205","tid":1018023,"uid":38030,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"中國網友則說，「外國人畢竟見識少」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b89c53e3b46f3ccfdaa57b539489b94de82d82","tid":1018023,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e23f4ea9d03c51d345f9d68d3eb0a908c85041a1","tid":1018023,"uid":63154,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"46e20e763b7bf57af999db37689268808fcf7205","tid":1018023,"uid":38030,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"中國網友則說，「外國人畢竟見識少」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"真係唔知邊個見識少，例如我未見過文明國家通街痾屎"},{"pid":"5692e64e440277743e6bbd079213dd749a7eca1f","tid":1018023,"uid":150363,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"46e20e763b7bf57af999db37689268808fcf7205","tid":1018023,"uid":38030,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"中國網友則說，「外國人畢竟見識少」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"大陸網民曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ab8410baf1a4f94db5c856efae700951bdee93","tid":1018023,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"自由戀愛呢樣嘢，你地D chinaman識條鐵咩"},{"pid":"a719925b6068c31466c0a63754f16f68ed9f0d8c","tid":1018023,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"職業病，慣咗問人「去不去？」匪語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}